      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "With our "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://www.eurail.com/eurail-passes/global-pass?cur=USD&gclid=Cj0KEQiA_eXEBRDP8fnIlJDXxsIBEiQAAGfyoSUXEFh4UMA8R73sB6-YdYEwOVs6gHJPOG4Hi65QHiUaAjav8P8HAQ",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "Global Eurail Pass"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", we were able to get 50% off the public boat tours on Lake Zurich. The prices vary by tour but the full fare price without a discount looked to be about $10-11 per person. Our tour was nearly two hours, and it was the perfect way to see the lake and the surrounding Swiss towns...."
