          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " Around the corner from the market, there are more shops, boutiques, and restaurants under the 36 Viaduct Arches. The arches are a railway viaduct that was built in 1894! It was neat to see how the city is using this space, a very cool mix of historic and modern. It's a great place to look around and window shop even if you don't plan on spending any money."
          }
