          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Swiss National Museum"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "We got free entry into the Swiss National Museum with our Zurich Card. Without the Zurich Card, we wouldn't have been able to fit this into our budget for the day. The museum offered an interesting way to spend an afternoon learning about Zurich and Swiss history."
