        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Delish Cafe"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "After all that walking and learning, we needed to grab a bite to eat. We ran across the Delish Cafe that was recommended to us by our walking tour guide, so we went inside for a snack and afternoon coffee. We were delightfully surprised to see how affordable several items on the menu were, and I definitely recommend this as a place to stop for a bite in the middle of downtown Zurich!"
          }
        ]
