        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Free City Water"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "One thing Zurich is known for is its excellent drinking water quality and its abundant fountains. Carry a water bottle around and feel free to refill it at any of the beautiful fountains you will see all over the city! Yes, it really is all drinkable!"
          }
        ]
